---
title: Paprika Spiced Cod with Herbed Potatoes and Garlic Mayo
description: At HelloFresh we believe that being short of time should never stand in the way of getting delicious looking and tasting recipes on the table. With its flaky, meaty white flesh and subtle flavour, cod is one of our favourite fish for an everyday feast. Spiced with smoky paprika and served with crushed herby potatoes and crunchy mangetout, this recipe proves that it pays to keep things simple.
